				<div style="font-style:italic">um, dots is a typo... I ment Zots...<br />
<br />
Zots are basicly development man hours... on a project you only have so many resources that can work so many hours on any given job (Zots) so you allocate them based on your priority list and what will have the greatest impact on the project.<br />
<br />
Hense a AE 'ring/cone' highlight for spells will contribute more per hour of work for all players than changing the sanctuary spell to some kind of 15second aura effect. imo anyway. <br />
Basicaly you get the same effect (lets you ensure all of the group are buffed) plus some (lets you target AE's) but the value is there for all players with all area spells rather than just sorcerors and just sanctuary spells.</div>
			
		</td>
