<br />
I'm still thing the Aura thing is not needed if we can just get a good idea on the target radius. Since the effect is only 15 seconds you would likely want to have it pulse every second, cause for such a 'emergency' type spell you dont wanna wait 15% of the spell duration for it to actually effect you once your in range.<br />
As it is they have slowed down pulses for bards/pallies because many 1 second pulses causes LAG. I think much of the performace boosts they have made has to do with revamping the code behind bard songs (which is also why they broke so many of them).<br />
<br />
Not saying its not posible, but it might be more painfull than just borrowing a mechanic from elsewhere.
                  
